{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"9561","heading":"Grants to nonprofit organizations that support minority business enterprises","label":"9561 Grants to nonprofit organizations that support minority business enterprises","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/ch120/schIV","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9561","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"Definition","label":"a Definition","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9561%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9561%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"is described in paragraph (3), (4), (5), or (6) of and exempt from tax under section 501(a) of such title; andsection 501(c) of title 26","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9561%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"can demonstrate that a primary activity of the organization is to provide services to minority business enterprises, whether through education, making grants or loans, or other similar activities.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Purpose","label":"b Purpose","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9561%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The purpose of this section is to make grants to covered entities to help those covered entities continue the necessary work of supporting minority business enterprises.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":"Designation of office","label":"c Designation of office","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9561%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"In general","label":"1 In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/c/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9561%2Fc%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Not later than 180 days after , the Under Secretary shall designate an office to make and administer grants under this section.November 15, 2021","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Considerations","label":"2 Considerations","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/c/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9561%2Fc%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"In designating an office under paragraph (1), the Under Secretary shall ensure that the office designated has adequate staffing to carry out the responsibilities of the office under this section.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"d","heading":"Application","label":"d Application","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/d","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9561%2Fd","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"A covered entity desiring a grant under this section shall submit to the Under Secretary an application at such time, in such manner, and containing such information as the Under Secretary may require.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"e","heading":"Priority","label":"e Priority","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/e","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9561%2Fe","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Under Secretary shall, in carrying out this section, prioritize granting an application submitted by a covered entity that is located in a federally recognized area of economic distress.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"f","heading":"Use of funds","label":"f Use of funds","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/f","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9561%2Ff","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"A covered entity to which a grant is made under this section may use the grant funds to support the development, growth, or retention of minority business enterprises.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"g","heading":"Procedures","label":"g Procedures","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/g","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9561%2Fg","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/g/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/g","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9561%2Fg%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"discourage and prevent waste, fraud, and abuse by applicants for, and recipients of, grants made under this section; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/g/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/g","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9561%2Fg%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/g/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/g/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9561%2Fg%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"covered entities with a national presence;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/g/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/g/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9561%2Fg%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"community-based covered entities;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/g/2/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/g/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9561%2Fg%2F2%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"covered entities with annual budgets below $1,000,000; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"D","heading":null,"label":"D","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/g/2/D","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/g/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9561%2Fg%2F2%2FD","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"covered entities that principally serve low-income and rural communities.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"h","heading":"Inspector General audit","label":"h Inspector General audit","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/h","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9561%2Fh","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/h/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/h","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9561%2Fh%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"conduct an audit of grants made under this section, which shall seek to identify any discrepancies or irregularities with respect to those grants; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/h/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/h","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9561%2Fh%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"submit to Congress a report regarding the audit conducted under paragraph (1).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"i","heading":"Updates to Congress","label":"i Updates to Congress","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9561%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/i/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/i","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9561%2Fi%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the number of grants made under this section during the period covered by the report; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/i/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/i","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9561%2Fi%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/i/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/i/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9561%2Fi%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the geographic distribution of those grants by State and county;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/i/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/i/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9561%2Fi%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"if applicable, demographic information with respect to the minority business enterprises served by the covered entities to which the grants were made; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/i/2/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9561/i/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9561%2Fi%2F2%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"information regarding the industries of the minority business enterprises served by the covered entities to which the grants were made.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}]}
